{"tid":811573,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高圖爾斯早想落「車」：不想做毒瘤","createTime":"2018-09-09T03:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T04:32:49.000Z","uid":161311,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ee04ed46216161dd8b6768be655c6deb41f8c39a","tid":811573,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:00:24.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里新兵泰拔高圖爾斯表示，早在3月已決定離開車路士，因為不想當球隊的毒瘤。<br />\n<br />\n泰拔高圖爾斯（Thibaut Courtois）在8月終於以3800萬鎊從車路士轉投皇家馬德里，他自爆早在3月已決定離隊：「之後，轉會差不多完成，所以我沒有向車仔報到，因為我認為自己不應該打擾球隊，我不想成為毒瘤。」<br />\n<br />\n高圖爾斯因為有離心，在轉會之前一直向車仔球迷批評，他對此表示：「這令我很傷心，他們不知道真相。」<br />\n<br />\n早前他大踩前東家，說讚皇馬的水準高於車仔，這名比利時國腳澄清道：「我只是說，皇馬在操練的速度更快，非常有質素，而不是說車仔沒有質素。」<br />\n<br />\n高圖爾斯指，轉會是為了回到西班牙，跟孩子一起生活，這對他是最重要的事。"},{"pid":"4861341be3a563b880eed1963b1fb86724f4fc77","tid":811573,"uid":58811,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:08:32.000Z","msg":"9up少陣當幫仔女積福啦柒頭"},{"pid":"fb86b1555a1fc00d1d067b2f171587da6118443a","tid":811573,"uid":133424,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:26:50.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係終極25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30d2771e96698d9587adcc7303d5f79f152a9b5","tid":811573,"uid":205462,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:40:56.000Z","msg":"做後備，但人工double, 係人都急急腳落車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c647b61517ecfe36f90562adf46fb3cfeffded4","tid":811573,"uid":106027,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"當年派迪布尼帽都知條友人格有問題"},{"pid":"569f6d621f1b1584a754dd67950eb11807303489","tid":811573,"uid":31585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"斷腳啦死25仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09233aa5d730bed7d6ad86abce7e8b2731933237","tid":811573,"uid":48381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:55:38.000Z","msg":"唔打擾球隊 但係轉會窗就完先黎轉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36595eb9fbef023e1735b071bd058e1e25cb6c8f","tid":811573,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"唔想啲人當你25就出少句聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下下提住車仔做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7699b2d01401d028aed73573fd6b9cbc9ef97dc5","tid":811573,"uid":144275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"當年竟然為左佢放棄施治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b319262039a3e2e76e37e72da647d3b7123640","tid":811573,"uid":197474,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"前車路士會長施治在接受英國足球報訪問中，炮轟高圖爾斯，稱他就是車路士更衣室的毒瘤。"},{"pid":"d14c4e3cf8207036fa8447f4462608a8a8405bd2","tid":811573,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"究極25"},{"pid":"99722ca0a6249ffb92864b9b65714b5c05d7b8e9","tid":811573,"uid":177100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"知唔知kdb條ex係咪佢老婆？kdb當年真係好慘，不過而家終於修成正果。"},{"pid":"bd9f02bef23061948d67f10c2d206be439bbc097","tid":811573,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84ec6d17b35483b1d2eed054f648085edfa840ee","tid":811573,"uid":161790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99722ca0a6249ffb92864b9b65714b5c05d7b8e9","tid":811573,"uid":177100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"知唔知kdb條ex係咪佢老婆？kdb當年真係好慘，不過而家終於修成正果。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201